column5: Dont forget about wan,ortiz and his brudder,,,,
I see you snowblowed a path already.Hope you make it out of the drive.    LOVE,N IT.  It,s the same here. Im happy happy happy.
Jeeze Wayne .. now what ya have to go and do that for ... I am going downstairs to charge up the sonar for the hardwater season ... unless ... perhaps just one more fall fat-girl session on GB ?
Plow just drove by my place..  Not sure why, cuz there's no snow on the road..  This should get the deer movin anyhow.
Probably brining the road.. going to -4 or -7 tonight.  Snow has stayed up here.. maybe the great white hunters can follow the tracks..
The brining truck drove by, then about 30 minutes later the plow drove by with the blade down scraping asphalt..  The plow truck drivers are looking to make some early cash i guess?
Nothin' here Wayne it just rained all night... It better wait until I can put some cash together for a new truck!
You seen that to eh. Waste of our tax dollars. Pretty mild this morning,me thinks she be melted soon.
Perfect amount!  Just enough to track and crisp the leaves up.  Hope you posted from the stand this morning Bri. Lol
Yup, them snow squalls in St Jakob's were fun.
Still out there Brian.. hard and crispy.. and you went to work, didn't ya !!
Love it!!!   We still have some left from yesterday & apparently supposed to get some more today Yay   I'm getting so excited for ice fishing & snowmobiling
Next friday cant come soon enough now.      Had to for a bit,then help the young son move. I,ll be out sat morn.
Well Andy and I will try to be quiet as we RIP down the laneway with the boat!!!
Andys coming to town? WOOT WOOT.
Scratch that... who forgets it's their wifes birthday.. LOL.. better now than after he comes back in the boat to changed locks!!
I would never  Im stealth hunting in the morning,you and leah keep the noice down ok?

Be forwarned.. I had my regular hunter come by the door for permission to follow thru and use the lower gate to the property. I said sure.. because he brings me crappie and walleye fillets.. what's a guy to do !! LOL  He doesn't hunt my property.. but does hunt the property on both sides.
I bring homemade cookies   . You want perch fillets too? LOL  Maybe go else where,as I dont want to ruin another guys hunt.
Like I said.. he does not hunt the property.. he only has permission to follow thru on something he has shot and it's bolted..
Ok.  I did a google earth on yer property.(yep I learned sumt,n new again)The trail is clear to the opening. Why Marty moved his stand,I have no idea. Great spot.
I already told you why yesterday, Brian....I couldn't get the feed there.
Easy ,easy Marty.It was
Well he could have.. but it would have taken Emanuel...
